  "time_ut": 1662015174,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 - \u0dab\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dbb \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0d87\u0dba\u0dd2?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Also find out about the Central Bank - Why did the loan default?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Mr. Vajira Abeywardena says that if we look into Sri Lanka's Water Supply Board, Electricity Board and Petroleum Corporation, we should also look into the Central Bank of Sri Lanka.",
        "Joining the budget debate in Parliament, he said that it should be inquired as to who approved Sri Lanka's debt default.",
        "He also stated that there is no responsibility of the MPs for this. \"Whoever asked, who did this, the Parliament should approve,\" he said."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "the Central Bank - Why",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
